Students will get acquainted with the procedures for admitting pupils to school.They visit all lessons and events during the first school week, observe pupils as well teachers and analyse their activities. Homework should be submitted in the e-environment.Objectives/eesmärkid:  To observe first-grade pupils' adaptation to school, to find out the most common problems, to observe different aspects of school readiness. To familiarise oneself with the duties of the form teacher at the beginning of schoolyear. To get acquainted with the documentation.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  By the end of the course a student 
*can observe and analyse the teacher's work;
* will know the main principles of assessing school readiness and observe the children based on the corresponding criteria;
* will be able to observe and analyse children's behaviour.
